```

**Note:** The `UUID_REGEX` helper should be extracted to a shared utility (`server/utils/validation.js`) so it can be reused. It is also needed for other routes that accept userId as a query parameter.

#### 1F. Tighten username regex to disallow leading/trailing/consecutive hyphens

**Files:**
- `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\server\services\uploadService.js` (line 42)
- `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\server\routes\routes.js` (line 866)

**Current regex:** `/^[a-z0-9-]+$/` (uploadService) and `/^[a-zA-Z0-9-]+$/` (routes.js)

